subsection.def:
Board
                    (管理局) means the Employees Compensation
                Assistance Fund Board constituted by section 3;

compensation
                    (補償) has the meaning assigned to it under
                    section 3 of the Employees’ Compensation Ordinance (Cap. 282);

damages
                    (損害賠償) has the meaning assigned to it under
                    section 3 of the Employees’ Compensation Ordinance (Cap. 282);

subparagraph.content:
if there is no surviving spouse or cohabitee, and no surviving
                                child, as mentioned in sub-subparagraph (A) or (B), any surviving
                                parent of the injured employee;

subsection.def:
employee
                    (僱員) has the meaning assigned to it under
                    section 2 of the Employees’ Compensation Ordinance (Cap. 282);

Fund
                    (基金) means the Employees Compensation
                Assistance Fund established by section 7;

insurer
                    (承保人) has the meaning assigned to it under
                    section 3 of the Employees’ Compensation Ordinance (Cap. 282);

paragraph.content:
who falls within paragraph (a)(i) of the definition of
                            eligible
                            person;

shall be entitled to the payment under subsection (1) or (2)(a)
                    notwithstanding that he has attained the age of 21 years or above at the time
                    the payment is made;

to determine matters relating to the remuneration and terms and
                        conditions of appointment or employment of the employees of the
                        Board;
